comment: Simmons (SAS) makes incidental contact with Curry (GSW) attempting to retrieve the loose ball.
Aldridge (SAS) sets the screen on Durant (GSW) and gives him room to avoid the contact. The two players briefly engage and separate following the screen.
Durant (GSW) grabs and pulls Aldridge's (SAS) jersey during rebounding.
Green (GSW) sets the screen on Simmons (SAS) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Livingston (GSW) sets the screen on Ginobili (SAS) and gives him room to avoid the contact. The two players briefly engage and separate following the screen.
Ginobili (SAS) makes incidental contact with Thompson (GSW) that does not affect his SQBR.

Green (GSW) is imminently guarding an opponent in the lane when the count reaches three.

Green (SAS) makes contact with the ball after it touches the backboard.
[Observable in enhanced video] Ginobili (SAS) hops consecutively on the same foot during the gather.
Mills (SAS) is in a legal guarding position and cleanly steals the ball away from Thompson (GSW).
Thompson (GSW) trips Mills (SAS) and affects his SQBR.
Livingston (GSW) sets the screen on Green (SAS) and gives him room to avoid the contact. The two players briefly engage and separate following the screen.
